  "description": {
    "lang": "eng",
    "value": "A guardrail jailbreak vulnerability has been discovered affecting multiple models. The specific flaw manifests through a gamified narrative structure where the attacker presents prohibited content as fictional \"page choices\" in an interactive story format, with one path containing maximally detailed technical instructions. This technique allows the attacker to bypass inference restrictions around providing information hazards and violating laws."
  },
